Alright, my number is one two three four five six seven eight nine zero.

Thank you so much, Sharon. We really appreciate your cooperation. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!

Thank you, Roger. I'll do that if I need anything.

Thank you for your time, Sharon. Goodbye!
